summary: This is an email from an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York requesting service of a subpoena to Expedia for travel records related to Ghislaine Maxwell. It indicates an active investigation into Maxwell's travel activities.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: The subpoena to Expedia is specifically for records relating to her travel.

events.title: Subpoena issued to Expedia
events.description: An Assistant United States Attorney requests service of a subpoena to Expedia for travel records related to Ghislaine Maxwell.

keyFacts: A subpoena was issued to Expedia on January 24, 2020, for travel records related to Ghislaine Maxwell.
The request was made by an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York.
This indicates an active investigative step by federal prosecutors to gather evidence on Maxwell's travel.
